name: LandWolfina
description: LandWolfina ($WOLFINA) bursts onto the Solana blockchain as LandWolf's perfect partner-in-crime. As his dynamic female counterpart, she injects fresh aura and style into the crypto community. Inspired by Matt Furie's iconic Boys Club series, Wolfina adds a thrilling new dimension to these beloved characters. Join our unstoppable Telegram community to embark on an exciting journey with Wolfina and her lover, LandWolf!
